sentence: i am interested in a flight from cincinnati to burbank [uh] the flight should be american and leave in the afternoon i need to know the aircraft and flight number
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  v0.flight_number, '"'||v2.aircraft_code||'"',
 v0.departure_time, '"'||v0.airline_code||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v5.airport_code||'"', '"'||v6.city_code||'"', '"'||v6.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v0.aircraft_code_sequence||'"', '"'||v1.aircraft_code_sequence||'"',
 '"'||v1.aircraft_code||'"',
 '"'||v0.flight_id||'"' FROM flight v0, equipment_sequence v1,
 aircraft v2, airport_service v3, city v4, airport_service v5,
 city v6 
WHERE (((((v0.departure_time BETWEEN  1200 AND  1800) 
AND ((v0.airline_code = 'AA') AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'CINCINNATI'))) AND ((v0.to_airport = ANY v5.airport_code) 
AND ((v5.city_code = ANY v6.city_code) 
AND (v6.city_name = 'BURBANK')))))) AND (v0.aircraft_code_sequence = v1.aircraft_code_sequence)) 
AND (v1.aircraft_code = v2.aircraft_code)) 
AND ( 1 =  1));
